<div dir="ltr"><p class="MsoNormal">Hi Folks!</p><p class="MsoNormal"><br></p><p class="MsoNormal">We&#39;ve been talking about&nbsp;<a href="http://blog.ushahidi.com/2014/02/24/on-improving-community-engagement/">improving community engagement</a>&nbsp;over the past few weeks, and talked of how we enjoy working in tandem with you to design, develop and deploy our tools.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">To do this, we need (and want!) to hear from you about what&rsquo;s working and what&rsquo;s not.</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">Please help us improve by taking a few minutes of your time to respond to our&nbsp;<a href="http://crwd.mp/CommunitySurvey2014">Ushahidi Community Survey.</a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">This survey will be open up till&nbsp;<b>11th April, 2014</b>.</p><p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><p class="MsoNormal">You can also share the survey with folks who may have some thoughts on our work and tools.</p>
